Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依铃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.55,0:00:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你又要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}偶尔也和我一起出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不要去别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说现在大家都在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.28,0:00:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小由 小紫 还有小春
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最重要的是阿夹也在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且你还没见过透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乐罗 别再谈这种对号入座的恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看着都难受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.19,0:00:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你为什么说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:34.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可这就是事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.88,0:00:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依铃 依铃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:41.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了 又吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽说已经收养她很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可她却完全没有融入我们家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.15,0:00:49.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:52.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才你说的别墅 你可别过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我听说大当家昨天也去那边了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可别出去跟别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.68,0:01:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是连你也被打成了重伤 妈妈我会晕死过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.10,0:01:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杞纱那件事真的吓到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人去别墅干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不清楚 应该是去避暑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说是紫吴邀请的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.23,0:01:18.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小紫 小紫你个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}乐罗 你还记得你上个月也把门给弄坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不会认输
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.83,0:03:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会不断前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.42,0:03:05.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会继续坚信下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那之后 由希没再说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.41,0:03:16.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们一起回了别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.33,0:03:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和先回到别墅的大家一起吃了松饼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.38,0:03:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希也笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我却忍不住想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.50,0:03:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}仔细分辨你代替语言涓涓流出的细声呢喃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:45.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}细声…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}本田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}波鸟先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么了 头疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:55.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才只是 那个 嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对了 波鸟先生为什么会突然来这里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天我和慊人一起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}发生许多事耽搁了 现在才过来打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以才特意过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难得和大家一起过来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}却留下你一个人看家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太客气了 您不用道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有阿夹陪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还像这样一起做了家务 其实挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:21.76,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没错 今天大家也去了慊人那里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我和阿夹留下看家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:37.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是波鸟先生他没必要向我道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道他是在担心留在这里的我和阿夹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道大家也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:47.79,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}做好美味的饭菜等我们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:48.48,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样想只是我的自作多情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.41,0:04:58.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我真是太幸运了 所以你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夹 要多陪着她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我最终还是不能去问候慊人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多亏了慊人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人到底对由希说了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:27.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.53,0:05:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是不是哪里不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的 我只是在想事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.16,0:05:41.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不好 连阿夹都替我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹 接下来要不要去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:46.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是去游泳 我们去玩沙子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那东西好玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 一定很好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦呀 由希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还以为你铁定是和慊人在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天轮到春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们可真闲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天慊人对你说了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说了事实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你满意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.00,0:06:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一点也不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}离满意还远着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红野也来了 是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算是真的也不会让你见他的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪怕是本田？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么这时候会提到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.82,0:06:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为红野也是十二生肖之一
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是十二生肖就必须见她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是你不让本田见他有点儿不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不自然？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}泼春总是会说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有其他你觉得不自然的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:24.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望你能不要这样笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.58,0:07:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.39,0:07:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是因为你这样 所以牛才会成为笑柄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.24,0:07:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 伤到你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我害你伤心了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.33,0:07:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说 这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是沙子做的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎么看都像是沙子堆的山
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:52.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}诶 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过我也没做过 不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是第一次用沙子做城堡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.35,0:08:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是说我是老师傅了呗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老师傅 你技术真烂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:10.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:13.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回来了 我回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓 吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:17.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红叶 你怎么又…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你俩怎么会在这里玩这种寒酸的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.26,0:08:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.22,0:08:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你今天累了吧 春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:30.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还好 倒是由希你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:36.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我总是害你替我担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:39.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过这次我真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.16,0:08:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自立了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.40,0:08:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真搞不懂你说这话时有没有理解是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 我喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喜欢什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:08:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.88,0:09:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我回来了 你一直在这边玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的 我和阿夹一起在用沙子堆城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哦 沙子的城堡？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还以为是沙子做的山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然由希也觉得是山吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:21.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天的事 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你应该很在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明知道那样会让你困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还净说些奇怪的话 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是不会因为吻了你向你道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我不觉得那么做有什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.84,0:09:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过你也可以把这件事忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么可能忘掉 怎么会奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:10:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这些对由希来说一定都是很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你昨天对我说的都是很重要的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是声音太轻了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你的声音是那么地轻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太轻了 以至于我无法听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无论我如何努力去倾听…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.53,0:10:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说出事实也要选好时机的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 终有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之 我现在能说的只有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:43.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我很好 不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.40,0:10:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透 由希
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像我被他玩弄在了股掌之间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但感觉由希突然变坚强了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:57.13,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我搓的丸子厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:58.39,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透 看这个丸子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.45,0:11:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 该回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.17,0:11:04.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你下次再见到慊人时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别像个笨蛋一样失控
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不知道慊人是怎么嘲弄你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}希望别做那些可能把小透牵扯进来的蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你凭什么对我指指点点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别在我面前拽 你算老几啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:32.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}啊 你 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}帅个毛线
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.42,0:11:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很轻的声音 虽然现在还很遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但总有一天能听到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说 红野
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不你去见见本田透？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}慊人和红野这是要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说是去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是去找本田的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个嘛 谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.11,0:12:33.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过慊人面对小透还真是优越感满满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}毕竟把我们都叫到了自己身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:44.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说到底 那个女人只是个局外人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.30,0:12:45.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孤立她就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且丑女的存在本身就很烦人 很碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}或许应该赶她走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过谁让我这人心地善良呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:13:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}给那个丑女带去点快乐也不是不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还想着亲自把你介绍给她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以红野你可要表现得像是十二支的一员哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你这方面不如别人 我挺担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之后那个丑女又要变回独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:24.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她在这边的这段时间 永远都是孤单一人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:29.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好好去体会赢不了我 比不过我的现实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她不是孤单一人 还有阿夹陪着她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和怪物在一起会开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:43.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}透
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.87,0:13:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}送你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是寄居蟹 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这次堆得挺像模像样了嘛 虽然还是不像城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:56.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:59.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不去游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不用在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我觉得两个人一起玩更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.89,0:14:14.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且我还想做一个超大的城堡 让大家大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那还真是远大的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.58,0:14:22.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过阿夹你为什么这么怕水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.60,0:14:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为猫妖本身就怕水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好像上一代也不喜欢水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}师父的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.16,0:14:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上一代也带着这串念珠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好神奇的念珠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是用什么做的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人的骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听说是一名高僧的遗骨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}很久以前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.82,0:14:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}红色的珠子据说是染了血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:00.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也不知道这些传言里有多少是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.22,0:15:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但至少可以确定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.20,0:15:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是用生命为代价制成的护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在我还是小鬼时 就曾对此产生过质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.59,0:15:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}需要牺牲别人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:20.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}建立在他人生命之上的存在究竟算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.42,0:15:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}夺走别人最宝贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.84,0:15:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}踩在脚下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即使如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:50.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓 吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还以为要被拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大海你个混蛋 看我不宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}搞什么啊 混账东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们打不过大海的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}别笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好悠闲自在的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.03,0:16:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明是个害死自己母亲的杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:19.56,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}话说你的帽子和寄居蟹去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.39,0:16:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被海浪拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.61,0:16:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们回去 热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:25.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}心情不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.93,0:16:28.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过我算是懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最搞不清楚状况的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是那个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.65,0:16:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还好 他们没有见面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢谢你先让我洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我现在可以去洗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.12,0:16:59.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没问题 我去把晾好的衣服拿进来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.89,0:17:00.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}牺牲他人的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一直戴着那串念珠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对阿夹而言到底有多沉重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}阿夹的声音也很微弱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.42,0:17:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对我来说很难听清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是我也有一些事不希望被别人知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:39.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要飞走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}太好了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有匹马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.29,0:17:57.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么有匹马在这
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.56,0:18:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是十二生肖的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.71,0:18:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}果然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:06.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咦 由希
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刚才看见你了 还在想是不是你就追了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是铃 全名草摩依铃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:15.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}依铃小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如你所见她是十二生肖的马
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:20.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铃 你怎么变成马了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.13,0:18:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}最好叫波鸟先生过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铃 你居然想在马的状态下踢人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:33.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要叫任何人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:50.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对不起 请用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这是靠毅力变回来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 我有一些更换的衣服就在不远处
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铃 不要勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你身体不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}没想会到在这里遇见新的十二生肖成员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.87,0:19:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是被马附身的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.41,0:19:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而且非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所谓的妖艳就是指那种类型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身材也非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.16,0:19:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿我的衣服给她穿应该不合身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:38.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铃 你怎么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我被铃甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}见某个人的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在哪里做什么是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}听好了 我来过这里的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不可以跟别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.97,0:20:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你要是敢说出去 我会杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你明明知道自己做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.61,0:20:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一副轻松的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说到底你也只不过是慊人的玩物罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:26.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准说出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不准告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个 等等 依铃小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}光着身子还能呵斥别人 真是服了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.86,0:20:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.39,0:20:45.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}总之 今天遇见她这件事还是别告诉别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.64,0:20:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好的 可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我也非常想追上去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是我必须得回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.62,0:20:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为我是偷偷跑出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}铃的事就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.01,0:21:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}抱歉 像这样来去匆匆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}由希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虽然我能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.81,0:21:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我会等着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.34,0:21:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}马也被我遇到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:47.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只剩下鸡我还没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:54.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.51,DialogueBK,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可恶 可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是说 慊人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.57,0:22:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}必须把夹带来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道暴风雨要来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可真是个好事的家伙
