Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.75,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}放出的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.09,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}将梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:51.80,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悄悄带进了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.84,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:59.06,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}你是否还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:04.23,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}在由心发出呐喊时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:05.69,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想再看一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.69,0:02:08.73,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:17.03,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}对自己坦率些最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:19.99,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur2}我会踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:26.67,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(150,150)\blur2}去实现你带给我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:29.17,OP3_CN,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(150,150)\blur2}请不要悲伤  因为有我守护
